    "text": [
        "Dear John,",
        "How are you doing? I hope all is well with you and your family. It's been a while since we had a little chat. I just want to let you know that I'm putting my old television up for sale.",
        "You may be wondering why I'm thinking of selling my television. It's because I plan on moving to a new apartment on the 24th of February. Also, I have just bought a new television and so I wouldn't be needing the old one.",
        "The television is a 32-inch flat screen which costs for $2000. It's an LG product and you are quite aware that items from the LG company are the bomb!",
        "Could you please come to my house this weekend so that you could see the television for yourself? I wouldn't be home in the morning, but you can come anytime in the afternoon. I would so much love to have a cup of coffee with you later in the day.",
        "Best regards,",
        "James"
